</ul>
<p>You can opt out of having your information shared with 3<sup>rd</sup> parties at the point at which you share it with us and when you receive any subsequent communication from us.</p>
<p>We may share your personal data with a third-party auditing organisation (ABC) so they can verify aggregated statistics about circulation and usage of our products or review our policies, processes and procedures for compliance with relevant standards. You can view their privacy policy by following this <a href="https://www.abc.org.uk/privacy-policy">link</a>.</p>
                            </div>
